Token.Abstract: The Bit6ThumbnailImageViewDelegate protocol defines methods that your delegate object must implement to interact with a Bit6ThumbnailImageView object. The methods of this protocol notify your delegate when the imageView has been tapped by the user.
Tell the delegate that the imageView has been tapped by the user.

Parameter.Name: thumbnailImageView
Parameter.Abstract: The Bit6ThumbnailImageView object tapped by the user.
